WEBVTT

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:32.616
and she asked Vicky
and 99 other older people

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:36.240
who had experienced abuse
to tell their stories on camera.

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:40.016
And I am Dutch,

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:43.016
so in the Netherlands
we are obsessed with the truth.

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:45.496
Now, when you are a child,
that's a great thing,

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:48.136
because you can basically
get away with anything,

00:01:48.160 --> 00:01:51.456
like "Yes, Mama,
it was me who smoked the cigars."

00:01:51.480 --> 00:01:53.120
(Laughter)

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:57.896
But I think this is why
I have dedicated my life

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:02.176
to promoting citizen video
to expose human rights violations,